reviews.review_text:
Great Show! I had a tape of the second set years ago and loved it.  The whole second set crackles and sparks, and this recording captures *all* of it out of the air.  Seems to have been a good run for the band - Jerry burns up the strings and everybody else is on! .    I assumed what I had of this show then was an A+ soundboard - but I think it must've been this recording.  I've not heard the soundboard - but it can't be as good as this! GEM indeed!

P.S. - The Alpine show that follows this [6/26] is killer too.  Check it out! Brent's crazed creatures coming out of Eyes and his post-Gimme Some Lovin' Gloria tease is worth the show, but there's more - Hyperspace China > Rider and Whoa! - Super Magnolia! -->  http://www.archive.org/details/gd87-06-26.bille.kerbel.8138.sbeok.shnf
